:AutomationController a owl:Class;
  rdfs:subClassOf :AutomationHardwareConcept;
  rdfs:comment "A computational hardware that hosts a control program. The hardware consists of a CPU which may be wired to input-output and communication network interfaces. Typically, the control program can be downloaded in to such a device or the device may contain pre-loaded programs that can be activated." .

